name: Cave Painting (18/07/2021)
description: An artwork in the Cave Painting Series by the artist M Plummer-Fernández. Created and minted 18/07/2021. This one is the first cave experiment using a cave as a starting point and slowing down the transformation between the two cave states. The Cave Paintings are produced by a custom neural network system that projects visions onto imaginary caves in response to prompts chosen by the artist.
